The recent Center for Strategic and International Studies report <a href="http://pcrproject.com/blog/2007/02/23/download-new-report-breaking-point-measuring-progress-in-afghanistan" target="_blank">"Breaking Point: Measuring Progress in Afghanistan"</a> can be read online.<p>
